# Factorial Method

```java
public static int fact(int n){
    int ans = 1;

    for(int i=1;i<=n;i++){
        ans *= i;
    }

    return ans;
}
```

Example

```
5! = 120
```

Time Complexity

```
O(n)
```

Space Complexity

```
O(1)
```

---

# Combination (nCr)

### Formula

```
nCr = n! / (r! × (n-r)!)
```

Java Code

```java
int ncr = fact(n)/(fact(r)*fact(n-r));
```

Example

```
5C2

= 120/(2×6)

= 10
```

---

# Permutation (nPr)

### Formula

```
nPr = n! / (n-r)!
```

Java Code

```java
int npr = fact(n)/fact(n-r);
```

Example

```
5P2

= 120/6

= 20
```

